# Code Style

## Naming Conventions

- Use kebab-case for folders and files
- Use PascalCase for React components
- Use camelCase for functions and variables
- Use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for constants

## Further Information

For detailed code style rules including import organization, formatting, and linting rules, refer to the @eslint.config.mjs in this project.
